      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and stayed on top of every single service. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels practically brand new without that dealership price tag, you\u2019ve definitely found it. Come take a look and see for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
