    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the 3.8L DFI flat-six powerplant delivering 385 hp with surgical precision. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers short-throw engagement with crisp synchros, paired with a limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The PASM-equipped chassis remains taut, showcasing zero bushing deflection or hydraulic weeping. Every component, from the four-piston monobloc calipers to the meticulously maintained cooling circuits, remains in showroom-grade condition. This is a turn-key example for the discerning purist demanding mechanical perfection and visceral throttle response.",
